Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:04.35,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, this is episode four of the spin-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.65,Main Dialogue Top,Girl,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:10.07,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Th-This is feeling more and more \Nlike a variety show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:13.30,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Right, and since we're approaching \Nthe middle of the series,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.82,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I'm thinking we should do a \Ncharacter song collaboration!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.37,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,A character song collaboration?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:18.55,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I heard they're going to release
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:22.04,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,an album with the main theme and \Nrelated songs from this spin-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:26.75,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It would be nice if we each \Nmade our own character song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.25,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,but since this'll be the first character \Nsong for the Charm members,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:33.97,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,it'd be weird to announce solo songs \Nfor a collaboration album, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:37.15,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I see. So we'd all collaborate \Nto make a character song
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.68,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,about all the members of the two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:43.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,And it's more fun if there are lots of songs \Nwe can sing together at events, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.77,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Makes it hard to pinpoint the tone-deaf singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:46.98,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:51.41,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,If we had a collaboration event without music,\Nthen it'd just be a talk event,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:53.65,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,which would put a bigger burden on us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.90,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,and they wouldn't be able to \Nincrease the ticket price.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:58.01,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,T-Tomomi-san, that's so businesslike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:01.31,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,So what kind of character song collaboration \Nare we actually going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:05.00,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Normally, character songs are like \Na character's theme song, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:09.43,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,If we do a song as a collaboration, \Nwe need a theme that we're all singing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:11.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,It's tough to decide what to sing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:13.17,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Agonizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.54,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Well, let's not think too hard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:18.23,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Collaboration is like a festival, \Nso we should just have fun with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:23.68,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's all think of a new character song \Nthat the people watching us will like!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.28,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,We can just feel our way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:28.28,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,It'll probably be a song that's sung \Nonly once at an event, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:31.51,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,so it's no use knotting our brows over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:35.45,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,And so, the Tesagure Club \Nmentality thoroughly saturated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:37.12,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,us apprentice goddesses, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:38.62,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:42.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Well, now that we've publicly made our \Nexcuses for the collaboration character song,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:44.51,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,let's have another fun collaboration!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.59,Main Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:48.96,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Huh?! Th-Those were excuses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.56,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I switched to a new smartphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:30.92,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,The phone as lovely as a work of art, \Nthat makes everyone smile:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.27,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,the smile art phone, or smartphone for short!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.48,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Was I smiling that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.93,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,And it's "smart," not "smile."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.45,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,What does a smartphone do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.82,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.50,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Wow... It's all-purpose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.87,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.23,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,So is it good with curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.79,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:54.57,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Even though Rin-chan is a gluttonous character, \Nunlike Koharun, her stomach doesn't growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.59,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Maybe the person voicing her \Nis more of a professional...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:00.93,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Th-That's not it! This is the scripted part!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:06.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Hey, Koharun, can you keep your stomach \Nquiet, even though it's the scripted part?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:10.53,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,I-It's not up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.24,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I still have an old cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.00,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,The old, clunky kind, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:15.91,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Clunky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.23,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Yeah. Heavy and clunky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.65,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.82,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Clucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.19,Birds Sign 2,Sign,0,0,0,,Clunky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.19,Birds Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Cluck Cluck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.39,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Chicken bone soup makes curry delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.12,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Y-You made it connect with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.29,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,These days, isn't it unusual for \Nsomeone not to have a smartphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.99,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,True. Maybe she has some \Nattachment to the old style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.46,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It's not that odd for one person out of \Nseveral to have that kind of phone, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.96,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Mobuko-san, do any of your sisters \Nhave the old-style cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:43.55,Main Dialogue,Mobuko,0,0,0,,We basically do everything together, \Nso there's one smartphone between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.54,Main Dialogue,Mobuko,0,0,0,,So if you need one of us, just call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.50,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,A shared phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:51.82,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,So what's Galapagos? Is there \Nany connection to Harpagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.69,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,You know Harpagus but not Galapagos?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.86,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Galapagos are islands. The Galapagos Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.19,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Have you heard of giant tortoises?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.44,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Turtles, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.48,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,They don't look like they'd taste very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:03.93,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I don't see the appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.57,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.84,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's kind of a premature opinion, Rin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:08.66,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.19,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Apparently, people really used \Nto eat Galapagos tortoises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.16,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.61,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Partially because of that, \Nthey're in danger of extinction now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.96,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I see. Then maybe I'll try putting one in my curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.69,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,She ignored the part about extinction...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.57,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Hina-chan, you're really \Ninto your smartphone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.89,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Well, it's new, so I don't blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:35.12,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,So I guess everything is \Nbetter when it's new, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:39.98,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,To her, I must be a thing of the past, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:43.15,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I envy how much fun she's having\Nbeing so immersed in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.99,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I guess everyone gets excited \Nover new things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.83,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Yeah. This isn't exactly a proper \Nthird installment for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:54.01,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,but it is like a third season, \Nso if we're not careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:56.91,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,the viewers might get tired of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.37,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,But there may be people like \NKoharun and Yua-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:04.21,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,who feel more at ease when \Nsomething is worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I get it! It might be the \Nsame comfortable feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:12.76,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,The mood becomes leisurely, the setup \Nof various things starts to unravel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.68,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Stale anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.24,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,No, please don't talk about \Nthis show like it's old bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:21.02,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Are there any new things in \Nyour life recently, Kanon-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:25.18,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Well, let's see... This isn't exactly \Nwhat you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.52,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,But these days, other than my school uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.08,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I never wear the same clothes twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:33.03,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That way, every day, I have a \Nnew outfit and a new outlook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.62,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,They do make a lot of fancy \Nkiddie clothes these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.50,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,They're not kiddie clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.92,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Is there anything new in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.69,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'd also say my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.83,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I outgrow them way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.98,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Like my bra...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:53.17,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I kind of wish I wouldn't develop any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.63,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,So I've got a lot of old clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.56,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Do you want them, Kanon-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.73,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,No need! In more ways than one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:03.74,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Do you often outgrow your \Nbra too, Hiina-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.82,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.57,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I haven't changed much since I started high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:12.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,That's right. Even if you get a little bigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,you can just adjust the \Nnumber of pads in your bra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.32,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Of course! Since it's mostly padding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:21.26,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Would you drop the "fake" setup already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.17,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,My character's are real!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.62,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You're not going to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:30.91,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You're not going to ask, "Tomomi-chan, \Nis there anything new in your life?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:31.93,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.45,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Don't hold back, just ask me, comrade Kanon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.35,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.99,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Tomomi-chan, is there anything new in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:49.38,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Well, in my life, no, but in my {\i1}height{\i0}, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.61,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I connected it to height.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.99,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I thought I'd be done growing by \Nmy third year of high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.57,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,so I'm shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.63,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Is this boring to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.41,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I'm laughing my head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:09.16,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Sheesh. Chest, height...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.21,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.87,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Are you in the mood for curry too, \NKanon-chan? We have a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.36,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:22.45,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Yui-san couldn't make it today, \Nso Yua-san is filling in for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.77,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.91,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Just switching one person \Nmakes this feel kind of fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:32.50,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Rin-san, I heard something that \Nmade me curious. Can I bring it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.36,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:37.90,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,In the original comic, there's a scene where \Nwe all go to Kanon-san's country villa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:42.15,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,but for this, they couldn't prepare models \Nwith street clothes for us, so it was cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.58,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:48.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Then as a memorial to the original comic, \Nwhy don't we think of a "new country villa"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.84,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Will that really be a memorial?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:53.09,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,All right! Let's think of a "new country villa"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.41,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:57.62,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay... Kanon-chan's "new country villa"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.24,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,She hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.79,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,You had to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.21,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.50,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,You had to think about my name, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.89,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:05.19,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Okay! Um, there are 30 toilets in the villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.17,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:10.60,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Aren't there times you want to go \Nto the bathroom, but it's a hassle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.73,Main Dialogue,Girls,0,0,0,,Well, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:15.71,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,There are moments when you think, \N"Someone go to the bathroom for me," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.35,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,But if there are 30 of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.28,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,you take two or three steps, \Nand you end up at a toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.27,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.72,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I bet the smell would be intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:26.50,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,But it would be good for when it's a hassle, \Nor when you have a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.31,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.58,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Or if someone from another villa came over
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.05,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,saying, "Let me use your toilet."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.70,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.80,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,So it's just one huge toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.31,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.21,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:37.05,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay, Hina-chan's "new country villa."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.01,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,They send you parts every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.01,Book Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Let's Make a \NCountry Villa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.77,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,You put together the parts they send you \None by one, and it makes a country villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.77,Book Sign,Hina,0,0,0,,Let's Make a \NCountry Villa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.84,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Like, they sell you the first door for 190 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:48.19,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Right, right! The door is 190 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.67,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,The initial price!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:50.97,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,And then it keeps getting more expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.69,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Right, because you've got 30 toilets coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:56.30,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,So toilets come for 30 months in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:09:59.92,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,That could be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.01,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,It would be fun putting it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.16,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.54,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,And you'd be happy when it was complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.32,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:04.96,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.63,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Okay, Rin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:07.83,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay, my "new country villa."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.17,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,The whole thing would be see-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.90,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,A see-through country villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.10,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,You mean... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.34,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:18.22,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,You want to see the night sky, right?\NWhen you lie in bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.51,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,That's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.52,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.26,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.54,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Rin-san, you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.23,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.23,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.53,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I apologize for making fun of you last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.22,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:29.66,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You're cute, Rin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:31.34,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Let's start our journey again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:33.06,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Is this yuri or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.48,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,What a development!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.77,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Wait, I don't have much experience \Nwith yuri. Will it be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.31,Main Dialogue Top,Rin,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. I'll teach you \Neverything you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.24,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,As you'd expect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.80,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,It's okay. It seems Kanon-chan \Nknows a lot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:43.78,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Okay, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.30,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You both seem like you'd know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,They were in {\i1}Yuru**ri{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.33,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.47,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.04,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.37,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Right, you were in {\i1}Yuru**ri{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.58,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,You sounded freaked out! \NYou barely got the word out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.61,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,You always say stuff \Nyou're not supposed to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I figured it'd be okay since they'll bleep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.54,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:58.66,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:10:59.63,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Bleeped out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.63,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Then you can say it as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.53,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:03.44,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Continuing, any other ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.03,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.06,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Then Yua-san's "new country villa"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Everyone's nude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.74,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Um, just listen. Hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:15.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,The family rule is for everyone to be nude \Nwhile they're at the country villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:20.01,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Then they're like, "Oh, you've really grown."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:25.27,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But I bet if the whole family were nude,\Nthere would be fewer arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:26.29,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.44,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Arguments?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.79,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Well, for example, the nude mother says,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:34.63,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,"It's hard to make ends meet because \Nof you!" to the nude father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:38.08,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But the nude father says, "Shut up!\NWho do you think pays the rent?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:42.60,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But both of them are naked, so from the \Nkids' point of view, it's funny to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:46.35,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,So even if the mother loses her temper \Nand picks up a kitchen knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:50.59,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,she would hesitate to stab her \Nhusband, because he's nude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.94,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I think household troubles \Nwould decrease that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Everything would be out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.02,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.03,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,That convinced me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.40,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Don't be convinced!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.05,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.65,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was a nice story!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.80,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Okay, I have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.99,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,All right, Tomomi-san's "new country villa."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.80,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,After coming back from the villa,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:09.50,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,you've become such a serious person \Nthat people don't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.62,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:16.67,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You can't see the inside of the villa \Nand it doesn't show up on Google Maps,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.67,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,This is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.60,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,but when someone leaves there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:23.01,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,they've become a serious person \Nwho never makes any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.80,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:25.22,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.43,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:26.43,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:30.82,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,So if you asked the now-serious person what \Nhappened in there, what would they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.31,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,"Well, why don't you go there yourself?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.20,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.28,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Then the person gives you a detailed map.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.63,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That just sounds terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.22,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,You're being led on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:40.78,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:45.74,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,So even those boys who loiter \Nin front of convenience stores,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.28,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,if they went in the villa, \Nthey'd come out serious, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.33,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,They'd start looking for jobs right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.70,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.99,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.76,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,What do you think about that, Yua-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,It was really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:01.01,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,If the other members had come today, \Nwhat ideas might they have had?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:07.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Well, there would be some dark humor,\Nand I'm pretty sure one would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:10.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,"The villa would be full of hot guys!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.31,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I know! I know who you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.83,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Um, I know the name of her friend, \Nbut um, her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Um, her name's Koharun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:17.52,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Oh, Koharun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.86,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,She keeps screwing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.46,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Whoa, you said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.69,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.45,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.28,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Don't say "screws up."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.14,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.35,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.32,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,We've got a lot of screw-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.73,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,We're full of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.74,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:35.08,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I'd like to see your club room once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.08,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Yeah, I want to see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.71,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I wonder what you guys talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:37.67,Main Dialogue,Ayu,0,0,0,,Definitely, come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.70,Main Dialogue,Ayu,0,0,0,,Like I visited here today, one of you visit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.20,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,We'll go one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:45.67,Main Dialogue,Ayu,0,0,0,,Come in one at a time, and when you leave, \Nmaybe you'll be a serious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.41,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,So that kind of thing really happens there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.22,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I'm going to become a civil servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.15,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.35,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Why don't you go yourself and see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.53,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.55,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.83,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,What are we going to do today, Yua-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:05.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Actually, starting this year, Tosei High School \Nis going to have a new school song,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:07.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,and they're inviting people to submit lyrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.66,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,so I thought we would participate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.91,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Write the lyrics for a school song?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:15.63,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,If the lyrics are used, they'll become \Na piece of school history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.62,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Comaneci!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:22.00,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,All right! But before we actually think of lyrics,\N let's think about a "new school song."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.09,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.28,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, Aoi's "new school song."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:31.05,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,When you sing it, um, \Nwild deer always gather around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.15,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:33.71,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Is this Nara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:37.57,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Um, even if you don't have deer crackers, \Nthey'll gather if you sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.39,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.02,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is they're attracted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.45,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I guess the appeal of the singing voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:43.32,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.32,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,And maybe it's sung at a frequency \Nthat's pleasing to the deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.58,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,"I like this, deer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.03,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,"Let's go, deer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:51.70,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,"I like this, deer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.30,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,"Let's go, deer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:54.58,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,"Let's sing, deer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.31,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,The deer are gonna sing it with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.77,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,They sing with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.86,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That's new!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:14:59.86,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.76,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,That's new, deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.97,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's new, deer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.20,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Is that new, deer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:03.78,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That's new, deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:05.93,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:06.63,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,All right, my "new school song."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:12.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,The school song is a love song.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.60,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,And a heavy one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.18,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:18.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Um, like, "Another day waiting for \Nyou in front of your house..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.36,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.16,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Yikes! Stalking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.60,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'm waiting, I'm waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:29.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Um, like, "When I think of you, I'm in no \Nmood to study. I refuse to go to school."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.60,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.45,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.60,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.09,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,How should you feel when you sing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.72,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Everyone sings it together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:36.88,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,People who go to school, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.62,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,And yet, just the melody is really cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.62,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.54,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Like "boom-chaka-chaka"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.03,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:45.76,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.76,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.86,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,"Boom-chaka-chaka"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.89,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Like a march.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.73,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,There it is! There it is! A new one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.38,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,That was the highest level of boom-chaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.62,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,There she is! Our leader! Our leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Our leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.36,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Our boom-chaka leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:59.25,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Leader, thank you for the new song!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:03.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,So while they're performing a march, \Nwe're singing a love song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.54,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I have something that may tie into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.73,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Then let's hear Hiina's "new school song."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.91,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,The music teacher who's \Nperforming it is so into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.66,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,he ends up smashing the instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.46,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Boom-chaka-chaka-bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.29,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Ba-boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.20,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,He's so into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:19.95,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Crash, crash, crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Like someone who destroys their \Ndrums at the end of a concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.35,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.96,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,When you get to feeling too good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:26.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.93,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:28.98,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:31.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, Koharun's "new school song."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.72,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,It's got cute choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,What, "boom-chaka-chaka"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.20,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,What kind of choreography goes \Nwith a "boom-chaka-chaka" melody?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.51,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Huh, what kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.31,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:44.36,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Boom-chaka-chaka, boom-chaka-chaka, \Nboom-chaka-chaka, boom-chaka-chaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.24,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That's not cute at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.35,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Boom-chaka-chaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.35,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Standing bowlegged...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.44,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.03,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Like radio calisthenics!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.03,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Radio calisthenics?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.36,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Boom-chaka-chaka, boom-chaka-chaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.83,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Kind of like idols...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.66,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Don't make light of idols!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.49,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Her real job! Her real job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.94,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,You little!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:03.82,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:09.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, um, let's hear the melody from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:09.57,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:10.09,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,It's very pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:46.30,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I don't know the melody, \Nso I'll just say what I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:46.91,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,The lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:47.44,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.21,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.31,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'll say what I want, and you \Nwork it into the melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.14,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:52.60,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:55.78,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,I don't really know the melody \Neither, so please take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:59.05,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,"It's a beautiful melody," is all I could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.12,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,It feels like a school song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.12,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,It's pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.76,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,These people are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:03.96,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Pure, pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.73,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,So we'll let Hiina take care of that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.65,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.80,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:08.90,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,But I want to put Kichijoji in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.39,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.35,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Kichijoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.63,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.36,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,What part would be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:13.19,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Kichijoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:16.28,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Ah, Kichijoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:19.15,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,But then the school's name \Nwon't fit. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.65,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,We should put in the school's name too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.54,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,To High?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:23.30,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Tosei High...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.00,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Tosei High.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Why don't we put it at the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.67,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Tosei High...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.67,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.59,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,It's unusual for a school song to open \Nwith the name of the school, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.26,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Tosei High... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, what kind of high school is Tosei High?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.40,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:38.93,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.01,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Confined...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:43.40,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.52,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:45.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.64,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Da-da-da...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.81,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Hot guys running rampant...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.06,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.94,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,What? What? "Hot guys running rampant"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:52.30,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Hot guys running rampant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.49,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,What does "running rampant" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:55.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,It means they're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.03,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.49,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Running rampant...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.49,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,My paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:00.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.87,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,My paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.74,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It fits. It fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:05.33,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.49,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Confined in my paradise with \Nhot guys running rampant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Totally masochistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.66,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Let's put a totally sadistic element in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:13.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.49,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Yua, I thought you wanted to \Nput a proverb in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,That's right! I want to put in, like, \N"what goes around, comes around."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Or "survival of the fittest."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.26,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Next! Next, "what goes around, comes around" fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.78,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.03,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,"What goes around, comes around"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:24.90,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,It does fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.31,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,"Survival of the fittest"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:31.27,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,La-la-lala-la-la-la-la-la...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.55,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,This is long, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:36.22,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,La-la-la-la-la...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:38.25,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,It's kind of a sad melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:38.96,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.18,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Should we make it sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:42.70,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Should we, um, make it heavy like we wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.04,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A heavy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:48.42,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Da-da-dada-da-da-da-da-da...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.43,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Only you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.61,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,What does that mean, "Only you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.14,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,So let's put in "Only you" there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Should we use "Only you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Survival of the fittest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.68,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Like, this takes place in a world \Nwhere only the strong eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Like, you and I survived. That kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.76,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,And like, meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.85,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Words that convey that nuance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:16.76,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Only you and I survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.97,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,La-la-la...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:25.22,Main Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,Ah, Kichijoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:26.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:27.98,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,What should we do with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:29.76,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Maybe something funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.44,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,"I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.69,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.75,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,No, I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.18,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,There's like, a conflict in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.71,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,So there's a conflict part?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.22,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Let's go with "I hate you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.51,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Start with "I hate you," then become honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.48,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.21,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Only you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:51.83,Main Dialogue,Yua/Aoi,0,0,0,,I hate you. No, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.60,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.66,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Then let's make it a boy and girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.32,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,"I hate you. No, I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.23,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I like "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.13,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I've got it. The guy should say, "Me, too..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.94,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, he should...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:07.35,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,"I hate you. No, I love you." "Me, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.71,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Ah, Kichijoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:10.59,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.49,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kichijoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:12.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,What kind of school song is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:14.13,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,I like this love confession part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.00,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,It's the most passionate part.
